data.description: Fully handicap accessible, spacious, 4 bedroom, 2 bathroom with open floor plan retrofitted to VA standards. Built in 2019 this home has added over 90k in upgrades including wider doorways, roll in shower, access ramps and automatic remote control front door with keyless lock. Home comes with stainless steel appliances, energy efficient washer and dryer. barn doors in master. Exterior boasts sizable concrete patio that wraps around the side of the home (egress): recessed lighting as well as new fans in each bedroom. Vinyl plank flooring throughout the interior, with solid hardie board siding on the exterior that will stand the test of time! Master has a very sizable ensuite that features double vanity sinks. Laundry has its own separate indoor area. Fully fenced in backyard. Seller is willing to contribute $2,500 as a seller credit.
